4 周岁的儿童可以购买儿童优惠票；年满 14 周岁的儿童，应购买全价票。每一名持票成年人旅客可免费携带一名未满 6 周岁且不单独占用席位的儿童乘车；超过一名儿童时，超过人数应当购买儿童优惠票。 值得注意的是，未实行车票实名制的，身高达到 1.2 米且不足 1.5 米的儿童可以购买儿童优惠票；身高达到 1.5 米的儿童，应当购买全价票。每一名持票成年人旅客可免费携带一名身高未达到 1.2 米且不单独占用席位的儿童乘车；超过一名儿童时，超过人数应当购买儿童优惠票。 另外，儿童优惠票的席别应当与同行成年人所持车票相同，到站不得远于成年人车票的到站。按上述规定享受免费乘车的儿童单独占用席位时，应当购买儿童优惠票。 据悉，此次意见反馈截止时间为 2021 年 11 月 27 日。 来源：羊城晚报重磅！铁路儿童客票拟由身高划分改为以年龄划分"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-6f93faa6d764c402cea4ea183300b3cb_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/495654679"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I18zQ2NKkwK0UEAMaCDcyNDI2Mjc0IIT594sGMCQ4uQVAGnIJNDk1NjU0Njc5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1635692531.4198003", "card_id": "Q_287378875", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 7894}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些你觉得是人间绝句的诗词？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-f7db1c83c2225ee60dfa7db621b4dd2e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/287378875"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI18zQ2NKkwK0UEAMaCDI2MTM5MTc0IOTD8toFMFU4zrYJQBtyCTI4NzM3ODg3NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1635692531.420108", "card_id": "Q_389251483", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 109}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "国产有哪些认认真真的跑鞋？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-768e1b0b76a014a112d3aa020287d142_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "34 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/389251483"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I18zQ2NKkwK0UEAMaCDQ4Nzc4MjYxIIaa9fQFMAQ4kwtAHHIJMzg5MjUxNDgze